The paper deals with object detection in satellite imagery, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV). The authors also introduce a novel loss function to address the imbalanced nature of the dataset, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of natural language processing techniques for image captioning, which falls under computational linguistics (cs.CL) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
